description:
This research protocol summarizes the methodological steps and results followed to conduct the systematic literature review titled "Gender Diversity Interventions in Software Engineering: A Comprehensive Review of Existing Practices". 
 In the README file we share the following information: 1. Data Collection 2. Data Synthesis 3. Inclusion and Exclusion Criteria 4. Quality Criteria 5 Data and File Overview 
 The files shared include: - Snapshot (.csv file) - Paper-Information (.csv file) - Intervention-Information (.csv file) - Research-Methodology (.csv file) - Publication Channels and Frequency Mapping (.pdf file)&nbsp;

